<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="let-alone-be">let ... alone / be</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不要碰；不干涉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let my things alone! 
别动我的东西。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let him alone / be. He needs a bit of freedom. 
别管他，他需要一点儿自由。</p></div></div>